summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6705 for the improvement of 2nd Ave. S. from S. Holden St. to S. Fontanelle St.; and certain other streets; by asphaltic paving; under Ordinance No. 107511, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
